text: Georg Krog (born August 18, 1946) is an American skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 1968 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1946 births Category:Living people Category:American male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of the United States Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 1968 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
